Merge pull request #24 from ainformatico/master

Fixes passing custom options to a new BootstrapTip instance

Fixes passing custom options to a new BootstrapTip instance

Otherwise custom options are never set.
Use empty string rather than .. for initial content

Merge pull request #18 from infernocloud/patch-1

Update tourist.css to fix QTip overlapping

Merge pull request #19 from infernocloud/patch-2

Update tourist.js to fix '..' being prepended to all tour tips.

Update tourist.js

For some reason, when using QTip, Tourist is appending my own content text for each tour-step to this default. So all tooltips had '..' before my own content. Not sure why this default is being used, so let's remove it?

Update tourist.css

Removing these lines of CSS means that the tour-counter will not overlap the "Next Step" buttons when using QTip
